original_title: อู้หูววเจ้าชายโอคหล่อที่สุดในทุกทวีปของโลกเลยค่ะ
overview: Prince Oak Oakleyski is reality is a movie director who is so handsome, even more handsome than all actors in every single continent. But Johnny Depp is comparable to him because it's the same handsome quality. The aristocracy of Prince Oak Oakleyski is superiorly dominant in Asia because Prince Oak Oakleyski is the only prince in Asia who turned himself to be a director-actor of movies. That's why he can domineer over all actors/artists/singers/business persons in Asia. Many Asian people idolized Prince Oak Oakleyski. But he said that people should not idolize him because the real perfect man in the world is the Lord Prophet Muhammad that is far superior to Lord Kandanai. However, not many people know that Prince Oak Oakleyski is just aesthetic title of Lord Kandanai the real sovereign prince of Eurasia. The simple universal hierarchy is that the lord prophets are all above lord kandanai, but lord kandanai is above people who are not prophets. Thank God, our lords were born.
tagline: Prince Oak Oakleyski เจ้าชายโอค принц оьклейский
title: อู้หูววเจ้าชายโอคหล่อที่สุดในทุกทวีปของโลกเลยค่ะ
